 
TOPIC 13 - Designing, Defining, and Triggering CSS3 Animations without Custom Libraries (Thought Library).

Designing
To design animations the proggrammer must understand the properties:

    @keyframes
    animation-name
    animation-duration
    animation-delay
    animation-iteration-count
    animation-direction
    animation-timing-function
    animation-fill-mode
    animation


Defining

The key part is to define the keyframes
Keyframes hold what styles the element will have at certain times.

Triggering
Need to bind the animation to the element